  <text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
    <body>
      <lg xml:id="TolC064">
        <l>avaitām</l>
        <l>peyar ai oṭu ku</l>
        <l>iṉ atu kaṇviḷi yeṉṉu mīṟṟu.</l>
      </lg>
    </body>
  </text>
  <text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
    <body>
        <head>Iḷampūraṇar</head>
        <p xml:lang="en">ed. <persName xml:lang="ta">Namaccivāya Mutaliyār</persName> 1931, <ref target="https://archive.org/details/dli.jZY9lup2kZl6TuXGlZQdjZMelJhy.TVA_BOK_0007521/page/49/mode/1up">49</ref>.</p>
      <p>
iccūttiram eṉṉutaliṟṟō veṉiṉ, vēṟṟumaikaḷiṉ peyarum muṟaiyum uṇarttutal nutaliṟṟu.
      </p>
      <p>
urai: appeyarē peyar, ammuṟaiyē muṟai; īṟṟa eṉpatu iv viḷivēṟṟumai īṟākavuṭaiya eṉṟavāṟu. avaitām eṉpatu mēṟ collappaṭṭaṉa eṉṟavāṟu.  (3)
      </p>
    </body>
  </text>
  <text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
    <body>
        <head>Cēṉāvaraiyar</head>
        <p xml:lang="en">ed. <persName xml:lang="ta">Ci. Vai. Tāmōtarampiḷḷai</persName> 1868, <ref target="https://archive.org/details/tolkppiyamcollat00unse/page/n67/mode/1up">64</ref>–<ref target="https://archive.org/details/tolkppiyamcollat00unse/page/n68/mode/1up">65</ref>.</p>
      <p>
        i - ḷ. 
eṭṭeṉappaṭṭa vēṟṟumaiyāvaṉa viḷi vēṟṟumaiyai iṟutiyākavuṭaiya peyar, ai, oṭu, ku, iṉ, atu, kaṇṇām.
        e - ṟu.
      </p>
      <p>
peyar ai oṭu ku iṉ atu kaṇ eṉpaṉa palapeyarummait tokai. aḵtoru collāy viḷiyeṉṉumīṟṟaveṉpataṉāṉ vicēṭikkappaṭṭatu. peyarum aiyum oṭuvum kuvvum iṉṉum atuvum kaṇṇum eṉa viriyum.
      </p>
      <p>
ciṟappuṭaip poruḷait tāṉiṉitu kiḷattaleṉpataṉāṉ oṭuveṉṟum atuveṉṟum ōtiṉārākaliṉ, āṉurupum akaravurupuṅ koḷḷappaṭum.
      </p>
      <p>
viḷivēṟṟumaiyiṉatu ciṟappiṉmai viḷakkiya peyar ai oṭu ku iṉ atu kaṇ viḷiyeṉṉātu viḷiyeṉṉumīṟṟa veṉap pirittuk kūṟiṉār.	(3)
      </p>
    </body>
  </text>
  <text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
    <body>
      <head>Nacciṉārkkiṉiyar</head>
      <p xml:lang="en">ed. <persName xml:lang="ta">Irāma. Kōvintacāmipiḷḷai</persName> 1997, <ref target="https://archive.org/details/dli.jZY9lup2kZl6TuXGlZQdjZM3kZpy.TVA_BOK_0008472/page/n105/mode/1up">77</ref>.</p>
      <p>
iḵtu oḻinta vēṟṟumaiyuṅ kūṟit tokai kūṟukiṉṟatu.
      </p>
      <p>
(i-ḷ.) viḷikoḷ vataṉkaṇ viḷiyōṭu ― viḷiyēṟkum peyarkkaṇṇatākiya viḷiyōṭu muṟ kūṟiyavaṟṟait talaippeyya, eṭṭē ― eṭṭu vēṟṟumaiyā meṉṟavāṟu.
      </p>
      <p>
viḷikoḷ vataṉkaṇ viḷi yeṉṟataṉāṟ piṟitōriṭaiccollai yēlātu tāṉē tirintumiyalpāyum niṟkum peyaratiṟuti viḷiyeṉpatu peṟṟām. (<num xml:lang="en">2</num>)
      </p>
    </body>
  </text>
